# Canonical URL redirects - All variations redirect to HTTPS non-www
# These 301 redirects tell Google which is the preferred version

# Redirect www to non-www (permanent)
https://www.brotherhoodunitedcompanyltd.com/*  https://brotherhoodunitedcompanyltd.com/:splat  301!

# Redirect HTTP to HTTPS
http://brotherhoodunitedcompanyltd.com/*  https://brotherhoodunitedcompanyltd.com/:splat  301!

# Redirect HTTP www to HTTPS non-www
http://www.brotherhoodunitedcompanyltd.com/*  https://brotherhoodunitedcompanyltd.com/:splat  301!

# SPA fallback - serve index.html for all routes (200 rewrite, not redirect)
/*    /index.html   200